description:
&lt;p&gt;We are inviting applications for the position of Registered Nurse within our surgical day unit here in Boston. The applicants will be multi skilled across recovery, admissions, discharge, outpatients and pre admission assessment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting to the Outpatient Manager, the successful candidates will be expected to demonstrate high standards of individualised clinical care to ensure the needs of our surgical patients are met within the clinical environment and provide excellent customer experience, whilst facilitating the best possible clinical outcomes. You will be working to provide exceptional care in a multi speciality environment treating both NHS and private patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your duties will include:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multi skilling across a number of clinical areas within a day case hospital setting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitating a number outpatient clinics in a fast paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for ensuring the safety of post anaesthetic patients&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The ideal candidate will have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;a strong clinical background in acute surgical care&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;demonstrable skills, knowledge and experience within the out patient and/or recovery areas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commitment and flexibility with a willingness to learn new skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;comprehensive understanding of relevant clinical standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;excellent communication skills and proven ability to work in a team&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In return, we offer the successful candidate:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;




&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attractive rates of pay dependent upon skills and qualifications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;




&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enhancements for unsocial&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;




&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Private Healthcare&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ongoing training and development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;




&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Staff discount and voluntary benefits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Life Assurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;




&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contributory Pension scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;25 days annual leave increasing with service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;




&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Uniform provided&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free parking and subsidised staff restaurant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;




&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
